PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: The stock market plunge is a sign of fear at this moment. Biden tries to give a motivational speech, while the stock market is still open, and it drops further! Illegal border crossings are at the highest in 20 years. The only jobs Joe Biden has created are the money-laundering scheme for Hunter Biden with the $500,000 paintings that people are buying, anonymously. Florida man receives 8-month prison term in first felony sentence from Jan 6 Capitol trespassing. Last year Democrats put up bail for violent rioters.
